{"tid":141443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懶得做research，可是賣糞個壇野，feel到成陣膠味","createTime":"2017-03-03T02:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T12:51:06.000Z","uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f338e618351f3328bfe38e3ece1878d5abf1337","tid":141443,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"The Asia Microbiota Bank既簡介:<br />\nThe Asia Microbiota Bank is founded by a group of three Hong Kong-based entrepreneurs who care about public health. We are advised by a team of doctors, professors, and scientists. This dynamic cross-border cross-culture team of scientists and doctors are working together to offer safe, effective, successful HMT for patients. <br />\n<br />\n由三位<strong>香港企業家</strong>成立<br />\n<br />\n真心想知，有幾多人係真係信有機構真心招募人去賣屎?<br />\n<br />\n我話比你聽，呢個可能性唔係冇，呢個機構可能真係需要收集人類既屎做研究。但你諗下，屎，有幾難收集? 大鑼大鼓公開招募，目的係咪真係為左招募?<br />\n醫學早就倡明，會唔會突然話喂，爭你個舊屎，可以研究到D乜成果出黎呢?<br />\n仲要真係純粹叫你放低舊屎就走，一星期三日，一個月12日，月入4.8K，平均一篤屎佢地支付四舊水。<br />\n四舊水，你諗下，到底佢地會招募幾多人黎痾bat bat? 當100個好未，佢地每個月要比48萬支出for屎，屎wor，唔係金， 屎阿喂<br />\n可想而知，儘管即使even佢地真係要請人比屎佢，請既人一定唔多，佢地冇FULL TIME員工咩? 隨時可以話份糧包埋佢地D屎都仲得，叫D員工帶屎返工，一舊屎咁重份量都有排你慢慢研究。由此推斷，係咪真係需要大鑼大鼓叫晒傳媒去報導佢地請人捐屎? <br />\n<br />\n係時候講重點。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得，招募人只係其次，目的係收集大量香港人個人資料，如果你想做份工，要先做一份問卷調查，第一條問題，竟然係問:<br />\nFirst Name <br />\nLast Name <br />\nPhone Number <br />\nEmail Address<br />\n<br />\n我知見工黎講比個人資料係基本，但人地請人唔會收集到大量個人資料，呢間野咁揚就唔同，比傳媒咁樣報導閒閒地收集幾千幾萬個apply，收工順便去痾舊屎袋四舊大把人爭lam lam利。<br />\n<br />\n最後可能真係會請人，請，十個八個囉，然後三位企業家手頭上有大量香港人個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037144def55bfc113c7b94387e5b517179f2e8b1","tid":141443,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7251eaa17f0932411248858aed11bdfa85977b34","tid":141443,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d756d2fd68b08719c5db018a60647ba4b341fda1","tid":141443,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6475ff1403d2f7773ef5fb0fed348608a23df7ce","tid":141443,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9d1fadb65e96479a6bb75d0d5de9cd2ce749495","tid":141443,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d046ea7da4ef084a515060c977142d28e4087c3","tid":141443,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:47:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#0</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">🇭🇰冷🍚王</span></span>"},{"pid":"a05a721d0c170ebd4a3e4992684b2c74ee8e1649","tid":141443,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"好似要驗身先捐得 <br />\n唔係人人走去柯就有錢收<br />\n<br />\n唔知個驗身係自費定點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8234c986a5d8c10e68ef3ba244e6ab2afbdba4e","tid":141443,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"認同。睇完真係得啖笑。<br />\n未計要搵人驗啲屎個成本  <br />\n<br />\n可能收集啲屎嘅樣本係可以trace到果班人嘅生活習慣同身體狀況，但呢樣野需要嘅唔係random sampling，無理由係人就請。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一開始以為係製造gimmick，平價另類宣傳，而家睇真係似呃個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28afe3ab3a6b77e38e88b2261d0ba3c202a8f65a","tid":141443,"uid":8129,"like":0